---
title: Chicken Gyoza Udon Laksa with Pak Choi and Carrot
description: Fragrant and spicy, laksa is a noodle soup known for its rich coconut milk broth. This vibrant soup contains thick udon noodles with toppings including chicken gyoza and veg, making it a fresh and flavourful meal.
